  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Lemon Slice founders\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100029344\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-w=\"1024\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17456f6c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FZ300vPwLQknp2Kmsax4ia6PjK13uqUKoNQMVBjntmq0jSP4UVJ9mc0GwytxJ3Va4I2OLjfKcErW53QYCO5Vkmicw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;text-size-adjust:inherit;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-style:normal;margin-right:16px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.3);margin-left:16px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__0\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;font-size: 12px;\"><em><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__1\"><span leaf=\"\">图片来源：</span><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;text-size-adjust:inherit;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-style:italic;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.3);text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-style:italic;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;js_darkmode__3&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;font&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;face&quot;:&quot;宋体&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;font&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;face&quot;:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">Lemon Slice</span></font></font></span></em></span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__3\"><font face=\"宋体\"></font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">开发者和企业正越来越多地在应用内部署</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">AI&nbsp;</span></font></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Agent</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">与聊天机器人，但目前大多仍局限于文本交互。</span></font></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__3\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">数字头像生成公司</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Lemon Slice&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">正致力于通过新型扩散模型为聊天场景增添视频维度——该技术仅需单张图像即可生成动态数字形象。</span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">这个名为</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Lemon Slice-2&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">的模型能够创建基于知识库运行的数字化身，可扮演&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">AI&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">智能体所需的任何角色，例如解答客户咨询、协助完成作业问题，甚至担任心理健康支持顾问。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">“在生成式人工智能的早期阶段，我的联合创始人开始尝试各种视频模型，我们明显意识到视频将走向交互化。</span>像&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">ChatGPT&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">这类工具之所以引人注目，正是因为它们的交互性——我们希望视频也能具备这种特质。”联合创始人莉娜·科卢奇表示。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Lemon Slice&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">称该模型拥有&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">200&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">亿参数，仅需单张&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">GPU&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">即可实现每秒&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">20&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">帧的视频直播流生成。公司通过&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">API&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">和可嵌入小组件提供服务，企业仅需一行代码就能将其集成至网站。创建数字化身后，用户可以随时变更角色背景、风格样式与外观形态。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">除了拟人化形象，该公司还着力开发能够生成非人型角色的技术，以满足多元化需求。这家初创企业正运用</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">ElevenLabs&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">的技术为这些数字化身生成语音。</span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Lemon Slice&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">由&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Lina Colucci</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">、</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Sidney Primas&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">和&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Andrew Weitz&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">于&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">2024&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">年创立，该公司相信通过其自研的通用扩散模型（一种能够从带噪声的训练数据中逆向学习以生成新数据的生成式模型）来创建虚拟形象，将使其在竞争中获得独特优势。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">\"</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">迄今为止我所见的现有虚拟形象解决方案都在为产品增加负面价值，</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">\"Colucci&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">表示，</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">\"</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">它们既诡异又僵硬。前几秒看起来不错，但一旦开始互动就会感到非常怪异，无法让人放松。阻碍虚拟形象真正普及的根本原因在于它们的表现始终不够出色。</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">\"</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">为推进这项技术，该公司周二宣布已获得</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">1050&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">万美元种子轮融资，投资方包括&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Matrix Partners</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">、</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Y Combinator</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">、</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Dropbox&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">首席技术官&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Arash Ferdowsi</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">、</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Twitch&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">首席执行官&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Emmett Shear&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">以及&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">The Chainsmokers&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">乐队。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">该公司表示已建立防护机制防止未经授权的面部或语音克隆，并采用大型语言模型进行内容审核。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Lemon Slice&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">未透露其技术应用的具体机构名称，但表示该模型正应用于教育、语言学习、电子商务和企业培训等场景。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">这家初创公司面临着激烈的竞争，对手包括</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">D-ID</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">、</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">HeyGen&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">和&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Synthesia&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">等视频生成初创企业，以及其他数字化身制作者&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Genies</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">、</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Soul Machine</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">、</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Praktika&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">和&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">AvatarOS</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">。</span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Matrix&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">合伙人&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Ilya Sukhar&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">认为，虚拟形象将在视频主导的领域大有可为。比如，人们更倾向于通过&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">YouTube&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">学习，而非阅读长篇大论的文字。他指出，</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Lemon Slice&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">的技术实力与自主创新能力将使其在初创企业中脱颖而出。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">“这是一个技术实力深厚的团队，拥有交付机器学习产品而不仅仅是演示和研究的实绩。许多其他参与者都专注于特定场景或垂直领域，而柠檬切片公司正采用在其他人工智能模式中已见成效的通用化</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">'&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">苦涩教训</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">'&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">扩展路径（即数据与算力并重），”他说道。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Y Combinator&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">的贾里德·弗里德曼认为，采用扩散模型使&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Lemon Slice&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">能够生成任何类型的虚拟形象，而其他一些初创公司往往局限于生成类人或游戏角色风格的虚拟形象。</span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">“我认为，柠檬切片是唯一采用基础机器学习方法、最终能够跨越恐怖谷并突破数字形象图灵测试的公司。他们训练与&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Veo3&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">或&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Sora&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">相同类型的模型：视频扩散变换器。由于这是一个端到端的通用模型，其性能提升没有上限；而其他技术的效果在达到照片级真实感之前就已触顶。该模型同时适用于人类与非人类面部，仅需单张图像即可添加新面孔，”他说道。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">这家初创公司目前拥有八名员工，计划将资金用于招募工程和市场拓展人员，同时支付训练模型所需的算力成本。</span></span></font></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__3\"><font face=\"宋体\"></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-style:italic;text-align:left;\" class=\"js_darkmode__15\">参考资料：</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-style:italic;\"><a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2025/12/23/lemon-slice-nabs-10-5m-from-yc-and-matrix-to-build-out-its-digital-avatar-tech/\" target=\"_blank\">https://techcrunch.com/2025/12/23/lemon-slice-nabs-10-5m-from-yc-and-matrix-to-build-out-its-digital-avatar-tech/</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "AI 初创公司 Lemon Slice 通过新型扩散模型，仅需单张图像即可生成实时视频数字分身，并获得 1050 万美元种子轮融资，旨在突破 AI 虚拟形象的“恐怖谷”。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "AI 初创公司 Lemon Slice 通过新型扩散模型，仅需单张图像即可生成实时视频数字分身，并获得 1050 万美元种子轮融资，旨在突破 AI 虚拟形象的“恐怖谷”。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了 AI 初创公司 Lemon Slice 及其核心技术——通过新型扩散模型，仅需单张图像即可生成实时视频数字分身，旨在为 AI Agent 和聊天机器人带来视频交互维度。该公司宣称其 Lemon Slice-2 模型拥有 200 亿参数，能在单张 GPU 上实现每秒 20 帧的视频直播流生成，并通过 API 及嵌入式组件提供服务。Lemon Slice 已获得 Matrix Partners、Y Combinator 等机构及多位科技名人共 1050 万美元种子轮融资。文章强调了其通用扩散模型的创新性，认为能有效解决现有虚拟形象的“诡异又僵硬”问题，并具有突破“恐怖谷”效应的潜力。该技术已应用于教育、语言学习、电子商务和企业培训等场景，未来计划拓展技术和市场人员，并继续投入算力成本。",
